        <p class="fs-body2 lh-lg fc-medium">WebSite will permit Entity Representative to export Company Content at any time during the Subscription Term and upon termination, but will have no responsibility to make such download/export available to Entity Representative beyond thirty (30) days from termination. Furthermore, WebSite shall not be liable for any loss of Company Content or destruction of data beyond this thirty (30) day period following the date of termination.</p>
